Several preconfigured Arachni Framework Profile files.

To see details about profiles run:
    ./arachni_cli.rb --show-profile --load-profile=profiles/<filename>

Examples
--------
Simple:
    ./arachni_cli.rb --show-profile --load-profile=profiles/scan-comprehensive.afp

You can also combine several profiles:
    ./arachni_cli.rb --show-profile --load-profile=profiles/scan-comprehensive.afp --load-profile=profiles/http-high-bandwidth.afp
        
Example scan:
    ./arachni_cli.rb --load-profile=profiles/mods-audit.afp --load-profile=profiles/http-low-bandwidth.afp -gpcv http://demo.testfire.net/
    
Creating your own profiles:
    ./arachni_cli.rb --load-profile=profiles/mods-audit.afp --load-profile=profiles/http-low-bandwidth.afp -gpcv http://site.com/ --save-profile=profiles/my-profile
